description: Introducing amFilm Premium HD Clear Screen Protectors for your Samsung Galaxy Tab 3 7.0-inch tablet.amFilm HD Clear Screen Protectors are specifically designed to fit your Samsung Galaxy Tab 3 7-inch and are made from superior quality 3-layer PET film. The HD Clear coating allows for optimal visibility and clarity of your display screen and will not distort the natural color panel. They also promise to protect the screen from daily scratches, dust and scrapes. With a self-adhering surface, the film is designed for easy application and zero-to-minimal bubbles during application. A squeeze card is also included to remove the occasional bubble easily.Works with:Galaxy Tab 3 7.0NOT compatible with the Galaxy Tab 4 7.0-inch tabletContains:2x Screen Protector , Micro-Fiber Cleaning Cloth, Squeeze cardColor:HD ClearApplication:Each of the screen protectors contains 3 layers of PET film. The first and last films are mask films, where the stickers are affixed. The actual screen protector for your device is the film in the middle. Please use the stickers to remove the mask films (NOT the stickers themselves).Warranty:30-Day Money Back GuaranteeLifetime Replacement Warranty
